    dc:description "Figures 29-35. Apion brevicorne Gerstaecker:(29-30) habitus lateral,male, female;(31, 32) male pygidium,dorsal,lateral;(33) tegmen dorsal;(34) penis lateral; (35) spiculum gastrale." ;
